fields.name: Category
fields.description: Favorite category, as defined by the user at creation time.

fields.name: Config
fields.description: Configuration of this particular favorite, which are driven by the Azure portal UX. Configuration data is a string containing valid JSON

fields.name: FavoriteId
fields.description: Internally assigned unique id of the favorite definition.

fields.name: FavoriteType
fields.description: Enum indicating if this favorite definition is owned by a specific user or is shared between all users with access to the Application Insights component.

fields.name: IsGeneratedFromTemplate
fields.description: Flag denoting wether or not this favorite was generated from a template.

fields.name: Name
fields.description: The user-defined name of the favorite.

fields.name: SourceType
fields.description: The source of the favorite definition.

fields.name: Tags
fields.description: A list of 0 or more tags that are associated with this favorite definition

fields.name: TimeModified
fields.description: Date and time in UTC of the last modification that was made to this favorite definition.

fields.name: UserId
fields.description: Unique user id of the specific user that owns this favorite.

fields.name: Version
fields.description: This instance's version of the data model. This can change as new features are added that can be marked favorite. Current examples include MetricsExplorer (ME) and Search.
